snippet.textDisplay: Amazing video, thank you for sharing . My 65 year old husband had mild covid and he never take vitamin D . He is isolating in one of our room. I am looking after him and extremely careful. I always take vit D, vit b complex and vit C. I was so pleased I did not catch it. I’m 63 and I believe my immune system is quite good.he is now started taking these vitamins. I’m glad he’s ok now.
